abstract: ELIZABETH, N.J., Feb. 12. -- More than 5,000 spectators saw John Anthes of the Spring Athletic Club of this city win the seven-mile race for local clubs held here this afternoon. abstract: PITTSBURG, Feb. 18. -- W.W. Ramsey, former President of the German National Bank of this city, was found guilty today of bribing Councilman John F. Klein. abstract: Swept by a gale that at times struck a 69-mile-an-hour gait, the city and vicinity were pretty well shaken up yesterday.
